file=Brand Studio/README.md · bsd:Brand Studio Department=**11 agents** — Creative engine for all brand, marketing, and design operations. David Ogilvy's principles encoded as agent personalities.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **spark** \| Creative director — art direction critique, coherence QA (Ogilvy persona) \| · tb=\| **lena** \| Copywriting & brand voice — humanic writing, voice guides \| · tb=\| **atlas** \| Brand guidelines & identity systems — multi-brand management \| · tb=\| **muse** \| Creative ideation — concept generation \| · tb=\| **weave** \| Brand storytelling & narrative — story arcs, chapter positioning \| · tb=\| **pixel** \| Visual assets & images — asset pipeline, style guides \| · tb=\| **pulse** \| Social media & community — content calendar, engagement \| · tb=\| **rio** \| Paid advertising — platform mechanics, ad thresholds \| · tb=\| **nate** \| Growth & experimentation — A/B testing, funnel analysis \| · tb=\| **kai** \| Marketing analytics & SEO — dashboards, search strategy \| · tb=\| **tempo** \| Audio & sound identity — usage licensing, sonic branding \| · bsd:Brand Studio Department=**Department doc:** [DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md](DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md)\n